{
  "texts": [
    "However, not every solution supports replication, high availability, disaster recovery, etc.",
    "SIEM systems are responsible for continuous monitoring and surveillance of end devices and network assets; therefore, it becomes important to examine the availability of fault tolerance capabilities of the SIEM solutions.",
    "Data visualization is one of the most powerful features of a SIEM system.",
    "Lack of interactive exploration of data and customization of dashboards can adversely affect the effectiveness of a SIEM system.",
    "Organizations often need to comply with multiple compliance regulations that provide guidelines and best practices based on the industry and type of data."
  ]
}